    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de intel-media-driver</title>

      <note>
        <para>
          This package takes a long time to build because it compiles code specific to
each individual generation of Intel GPUs and for a variety of media codecs.
        </para>
      </note>

      <para>
        Instale <application>intel-media-driver</application> executando os
seguintes comandos:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr   \
      -DINSTALL_DRIVER_SYSCONF=OFF  \
      -DBUILD_TYPE=Release          \
      -Wno-dev ..                   &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
      </para>

      <para>
        Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

